        "text": "Counsel. The submission invokes Article 6. This is a civil court hearing a civil matter. Distinguish the criminal-procedure shorthand from the procedural-fairness right counsel is actually claiming. Why does Article 6 reach a civil eviction at all, and what does it require of this bench today?",
