            "flavor_line": "Article 6 is not a criminal ornament. It is the right to be in the room when one's matter is heard. Two facts on this record: a 2015 renumbering the municipality recorded, and notice that reached the client on the twenty-eighth of April. The client was not in the room. KPC Article 135-bis § 2 is the door back."
