            "judicial_patience_delta_on_miss": -1,
            "judicial_patience_delta_on_backfire": -2,
            "flavor_line": "Four elements, in the order the statute contemplates. First, the petition's address was renumbered in 2015 and the municipality has the instrument on file. Second, the petitioner himself corresponded on the corrected address — he knew. Third, the client received the notice on the twenty-eighth of April and the motion is within the window. Fourth, the recipient at number seven is the new tenant, not an authorised agent. KPC Article 135-bis § 2. The hearing did not happen because the client was not at it."
