          "result_text": "The bench grants the motion on the procedural floor. The order will be read as written: KPC Article 135-bis § 2, defective service, hearing restored. The judge adds, for the record, that counsel made arguments the court did not need to reach today and would prefer not to have been asked to. The remedy is the rehearing on the merits in the ordinary course. The merits remain open."
